UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2637
1 124.
2 Section 9. This honorable body declares that it rejects the Kentucky Supreme
3 Court's unconstitutional opinion and order of April 6, 2026, as precedent that should
4 guide its exercise of its impeachment power in the future.
5 Section 10. This honorable body declares that it has the sole authority to tax
6 costs, attorney's fees, or other expenses in relation to impeachments, that no costs,
7 attorney's fees, or other expenses shall be taxed or assessed related to any impeachment
8 or impeachment petition presented to or considered by the 2026 Regular Session of the
9 General Assembly, and that any attempt to do so is void.
